    function setAttributeOnload(object, attribute, val) {
      if(window.addEventListener) {
        window.addEventListener('load',
          function(){ object[attribute] = val; }, false);
      } else {
        window.attachEvent('onload', function(){ object[attribute] = val; });
      }
    }

Necesitamos tener esta clara compresiÃ³n&nbsp;&nbsp;para dirigir, para orientar la lucha de masas en nuestro paÃ­s, para que no se dejen uncir al carro de la reacciÃ³n y el revisionismo, que quieren atarlas tras el programa de la gran burguesÃ­a compradora o de la burocrÃ¡tica para llevar a cabo sus fracasadas tareas reaccionarias. La reacciÃ³n y el revisionismo, especialmente la LOD revisionista y capitulacionista, tratan de ocultar el verdadero carÃ¡cter de clase de las contradicciones interreaccionarias, llamÃ¡ndola de diferentes maneras, para arrastrar a las masas tras salida reaccionaria a la crisis de todos lo ordenes que corroe a su sistema agonizante herido de muerte. En este caso, a la agudizacion de su crisis polÃ­tica. Salidas reaccionarias como las que estamos viendo de &#8220;autogolpe&#8221; del gobierno reaccionario encabezado por Castillo que se ha quedado solo con el apoyo del Modavef o &#8220;bloque magisterial&#8221; (LOD r y c) en el parlamento y en las calles, y los del llamado &#8220;contragolpe&#8221; parlamentario por una conjunciÅ de fuerzas de ambas facciones donde estÃ¡n fujimoristas, PerÃº Libre con los CerrÃ³n a la cabeza y tambiÃ©n el ex-premier Bellido, etc.</span></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="ES" style="background-color: red;"><o:p><span style="color: #ffa400; font-family: arial; font-size: medium;">&nbsp;</span></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="ES" style="background-color: red;"><span style="color: #ffa400; font-family: arial; font-size: medium;">Pero para hacer esto tenemos que partir precisamente del marxismo-leninismo-maoismo, pensamiento gonzalo.</span></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="ES" style="background-color: red;"><o:p><span style="color: #ffa400; font-family: arial; font-size: medium;">&nbsp;</span></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="background-color: red; color: #ffa400; font-family: arial; font-size: medium;"><span lang="ES">La sociedad peruana semifeudal y semicolonial sobre la cual se desenvuelve un capitalismo burocrÃ¡tico. Desde 1980 esta en su tercer momento, de crisis general del capitalismo burocrÃ¡tico y de su destrucciÃ³n final</span><span lang="ES">, momento que se inicia con la guerra popular dirigida por el&nbsp;</span><span lang="ES">Partido Comunista del PerÃº,</span><span lang="ES">&nbsp;como bestia agonizante se defenderÃ¡ buscando aplastar la revoluciÃ³n. Le espera un proceso penal por intentar dar un golpe de Estado, un delito que tiene una pena de entre 10 y 20 aÃ±os.<b style="box-sizing: inherit; line-height: inherit;">&nbsp;El gobierno de MÃ©xico le ha ofrecido asilo.<o:p></o:p></b></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><b><span lang="ES" style="background: rgb(255, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0.1pt;"><o:p><span style="color: #ffa400; font-family: arial; font-size: medium;">&nbsp;</span></o:p></span></b></p><p style="background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial; margin: 0cm 0cm 15pt;"><span lang="EN-US" style="background-color: red; letter-spacing: 0.1pt;"><span style="color: #ffa400; font-family: arial; font-size: medium;">Resulta inexplicable cÃ³mo Castillo se lanzÃ³ a anunciar el cierre del Congreso<b style="box-sizing: inherit; line-height: inherit;">&nbsp;sin tener respaldo para sostener esa decisiÃ³n.</b>&nbsp;Se quedÃ³ solo inmediatamente despuÃ©s de hacer ese anuncio.<b style="box-sizing: inherit; line-height: inherit;">&nbsp;Sus ministros comenzaron a renunciar uno tras otro</b>&nbsp;denunciando que rechazaban lo que calificaron como un golpe de Estado. QuiÃ©n va a decidir? Las fuerzas armadas a travÃ©s de la manifestaciÃ³n de su Comando Conjunto. Dias anteriores se conociÃ³ el fracaso de Castillo de lograr el respaldo de las fuerzas armadas, lo que quedÃ³ patente con la renuncia de su ministro de Defensa. Esta ya habÃ­a decidido los dÃ­as anteriores, pero las tres horas de espera por ambas partes muestra que esperaban lo que llaman &#8220;la reacciÃ³n de la calle&#8221;. Como esa fue bastante escasa por ambos lados, debido al desprestigio de todas las intituciones y representantes del viejo Estado, los militares se pronunciaron, es decir participaron abiertamente en el golpe &#8220;parlamentario&#8221;, lo cual queda demostrado con las fuerzas que detienen al contrarrevolucionario ex-presidente Castillo, las propias fuerzas militares de seguridad presidencial lo detienen cuando se encaminaba a la embajada de MÃ©xoico.</span><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="background-color: red; ejerciendo constantemente su dictadura de clase (de gran burguesÃ­a y terratenientes), ya sea mediante un gobierno militar de facto... o mediante gobiernos surgidos de elecciones y llamados constitucionales..." y "...caduco sistema de explotaciÃ³n dominante destruye y sofrena las poderosas fuerzas creadoras del pueblo, las Ãºnicas fuerzas capaces de la mÃ¡s profunda transformaciÃ³n revolucionaria...</span></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="background-color: red; color: #ffa400; font-family: arial; font-size: large;">A la vez diferencia entre sistema de Estado y sistema de gobierno, que son partes de una unidad; siendo el primero el lugar que ocupan las clases dentro del Estado y el segundo la forma en que se organiza el Poder, como lo enseÃ±a el Presidente Mao, destacando que lo principal es definir el carÃ¡cter de clase de un Estado ya que las formas de gobierno que introduzcan pueden ser civil o militar, con elecciones o de facto, demoliberal o fascista y siempre representarÃ¡n la dictadura de las clases reaccionarias; al no ver asÃ­ el viejo Estado se cae en el error de identificar dictadura con rÃ©gimen militar y pensar que un gobierno civil no es dictadura poniÃ©ndose a la cola de una de las facciones de la gran burguesÃ­a tras el cuento de "defender la democracia" o "cuidarse de los golpes militares", posiciones que en vez de destruir el viejo Estado lo sostienen y defienden, tal es el caso de los revisionistas y oportunistas de la Izquierda Unida.</span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="background-color: red; color: #ffa400; font-family: arial; font-size: medium;"><span lang="ES"><br />Viejo Estado sometido al imperialismo, yanqui principalmente en nuestro caso, sostenido en su columna vertebral que son las fuerzas armadas reaccionarias y que cuenta con una burocracia cada vez mÃ¡s creciente; teniendo las fuerzas armadas el mismo carÃ¡cter del Estado que sostienen y defienden".<br /><br />El Presidente Gonzalo claramente nos dice: "Y es Ã©ste el sistema social que usufructÃºan y defienden a sangre y fuego las clases dominantes y su amo imperialista yanqui, mediante su&nbsp;<u>Estado terrateniente-burocrÃ¡tico sustentado en su fuerza armada reaccionaria</u>; ejerciendo constantemente su dictadura de clase (de gran burguesÃ­a y terratenientes), ya sea mediante un gobierno militar de facto... o mediante gobiernos surgidos de elecciones y llamados constitucionales..." y "...caduco sistema de explotaciÃ³n dominante destruye y sofrena las poderosas fuerzas creadoras del pueblo, las Ãºnicas fuerzas capaces de la mÃ¡s profunda transformaciÃ³n revolucionaria...".</span><span lang="ES"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="ES" style="background-color: red;"><o:p><span style="color: #ffa400; font-family: arial; font-size: medium;">&nbsp;</span></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="ES" style="background-color: red;"><span style="color: #ffa400; font-family: arial; font-size: medium;">Ahora, tendremos un gobierno reaccionario de Dina Boluarte que ha quedado<span style="background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial;">&nbsp;cautivo de las fuerzas armadas y del parlamento de mayorÃ­a de la facciÃ³n compradora. Nuevamente serÃ¡ un gobierno dÃ©bil, con similares condiciones y caracterÃ­sticas de depuesto, condenado a fracasar en sus tres tareas reaccionarias: reestructurar el Estado, reimpulsar el capitalismo burocrÃ¡tico y aniquilar la guerra popular. Por lo que, la honda crisis polÃ­tica del viejo Estado se irÃ¡ acentuando.</span></span></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="ES" style="background-color: red;"><o:p><span style="color: #ffa400; font-family: arial; font-size: medium;">&nbsp;</span></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 7.8pt 0cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="background-color: red; color: #ffa400; font-family: arial; font-size: medium;"><span lang="ES" style="background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial;">Tener en cuenta que lo que ha facilitado el golpe de estado es el hecho que las masas comienzan a moverse fuertemente demandando reivindicaciones, como en el pasado ante la carestÃ­a&nbsp;&nbsp;y la alza de precios</span><span lang="ES">. La masa entonces estÃ¡n entrando pues en efervesencia, todo eso bajo un gobierno dÃ©bil,&nbsp;<span style="background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial;">fracasado como el de Castillo, que no cumpliÃ³, ni podÃ­a cumplir sus promesas electorales. Pero, la situaciÃ³n no cambia mucho para la reacciÃ³n, sus dificultades se acrecentarÃ¡, Eso es bueno para la revoluciÃ³n, es bueno para avanzar en la tarea de la reorganizaciÃ³n general del Partido en y para la guerra popular. En situaciones como Ã©sta, con recambio de gobierno, sabiendo que el nuevo gobierno serÃ¡ mucho peor para las masas, hay que movilizarla para la lucha por la defensa de sus derechos, libertades y beneficios conquistados con sangre para elevarla a lucha polÃ­tica, esto es para cumplir la tarea pendiente y continuar desarrollando la revoluciÃ³n de nueva democracia con guerra popular.</span><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 7.8pt 0cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="background-color: red; color: #ffa400; font-family: arial;"><span lang="ES"><span style="background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial; font-size: medium;"><br /></span></span></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 7.8pt 0cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="background-color: red; color: #ffa400; font-family: arial;"><span lang="ES"><span style="background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial; font-size: medium;">Movimiento Popular PerÃº</span></span></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 7.8pt 0cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="background-color: red; color: #ffa400; font-family: arial;"><span lang="ES"><span style="background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial; font-size: medium;">08 de diciembre de 2022</span></span></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="ES" style="background-color: red;"><o:p><span style="color: #ffa400; font-family: arial; font-size: medium;">&nbsp;</span></o:p></span></p><div style="clear: both;"></div></div><div class="post-footer" style="background-color: #e50000; color: #ffcc33; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, FreeSans, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6; margin: 1.5em 0px 0px;"><div class="post-footer-line post-footer-line-1"><span class="post-author vcard" style="margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 1em;">Posted by&nbsp;<span class="fn" itemprop="author" itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"><a class="g-profile" href="https://www.blogger.com/profile/17515623922181723328" rel="author" style="color: #ffcc33; text-decoration-line: none;" title="author profile"><span itemprop="name">Verein der Neuen Demokratie</span>&nbsp;</a></span></span></div></div>

<div class='post hentry uncustomized-post-template' itemprop='blogPost' itemscope='itemscope' itemtype='http://schema.org/BlogPosting'>
<meta content='https://www.redspark.nu/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/FB_IMG_1596024112511-800x445.jpg' itemprop='image_url'/>
<meta content='1060677886973972614' itemprop='blogId'/>
<meta content='5471640832500754089' itemprop='postId'/>
<a name='5471640832500754089'></a>
<h3 class='post-title entry-title' itemprop='name'>
<a href='http://dazibaorojo08.blogspot.com/2022/12/india-18-international-hros-petition.html'>INDIA: 18 International HRO&#8217;s Petition CJI On Behalf Of Political Prisoner Dr G N Saibaba</a>
</h3>
<div class='post-header'>
<div class='post-header-line-1'></div>
</div>
<div class='post-body entry-content' id='post-body-5471640832500754089' itemprop='description articleBody'>
<p><br /></p><div class="post-body entry-content" id="post-body-238218343988182748" itemprop="description articleBody" style="background-color: white; color: #333333; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, FreeSans, sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px; line-height: 1.4; position: relative; width: 578px;"><div class="featured-image"><img alt="" class="attachment-colormag-featured-image size-colormag-featured-image wp-post-image" height="301" src="https://www.redspark.nu/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/FB_IMG_1596024112511-800x445.jpg" width="540" /></div><div class="above-entry-meta"><span class="cat-links"><br /></span></div><header class="entry-header"><h1 class="entry-title" style="margin: 0px; position: relative;">18 International HRO&#8217;s Petition CJI On Behalf Of Political Prisoner Dr G N Saibaba</h1></header><div class="below-entry-meta">&nbsp;<span class="posted-on"><a href="https://www.redspark.nu/en/peoples-war/18-international-hros-petition-cji-on-behalf-of-political-prisoner-dr-g-n-saibaba/" rel="bookmark" style="color: #993333; text-decoration-line: none;" title="8:47 pm"></a></span></div><p><strong>Mumbai, December 6, 2022:&nbsp;</strong>Eighteen international human rights organizations wrote a letter to Chief Justice of India D.Y. Chandrachud, expressing concern over the health of professor G.N. Saibaba and urging him to review the order suspending his release from the Nagpur Central Jail.</p><p>On October 14 this year, the Bombay High Court ordered the release of Saibaba, who is wheelchair-bound and 90% disabled, after eight years of a procedural lapse during his prosecution. However, the next day, the Supreme Court granted an urgent hearing to the Maharashtra government&#8217;s appeal and suspended his release. Prof. Saibaba was arrested on May 9, 2014, from the campus of Delhi University and on March 7, 2017, he was sentenced to life imprisonment under the Unlawful Activities Prevention Act (UAPA) on charges of &#8220;being a member of a terrorist gang or organization&#8221;. He is suffering from 19 separate medical conditions, including post-polio syndrome, pancreatitis and gallbladder stones.</p><p>The organizations are Scholars at Risk, International Solidarity for Academic Freedom in India, Freedom Now, Norwegian Students&#8217; and Academics&#8217; International Assistance Fund, Southern Illinois Democratic Socialists of America, Hindus for Human Rights, India Labor Solidarity, Coalition for Justice in India, Indian Workers Association, South Asia Solidarity Group, Turbine Bagh, Stichting the London Story, Anti-Caste Discrimination Alliance, The Humanism Project, India Justice Project, Free Saibaba Coalition, Coalition Against Fascism in India, Jericho Movement Boston, India Civil Watch International wrote this letter to the CJI on December 5.</p><p class="_yeti_done">The letter mentions, &#8220;Just a few months ago, Pandu Narote, who was convicted alongside Professor Saibaba, died in prison after contracting swine flu and reportedly being denied medical attention. We are deeply concerned about Professor Saibaba&#8217;s health should he remain in prison and not receive appropriate care.&#8221; The letter read, &#8220;Professor Saibaba was subject to arrest, prosecution, and detention in retaliation for his nonviolent exercise of the rights to freedom of expression and freedom of association&#8212;conduct that is expressly protected under international human rights instruments including the Universal Declaration of Human Rights and the International Covenant on Civil and Political Rights, to which India is a party.&#8221;</p><p class="atd-ad">The organizations urge the CJI &#8220;to review Professor Saibaba&#8217;s case and reinstate the High Court&#8217;s order so he may be released and finally receive the medical care he urgently needs.&#8221;</p></div>
<div style='clear: both;'></div>
</div>

<h3 class='post-title entry-title' itemprop='name'>
<a href='http://dazibaorojo08.blogspot.com/2022/12/india-celebrate-22nd-anniversary-of.html'>INDIA: Celebrate the 22nd Anniversary of PLGA! Intensify Class struggle-Guerrilla war Defeat &#8216;SAMADHAN&#8217; offensive and Advance People&#8217;s War! &#8211; CPI(Maoist)&#160;CC (ICSPWI)</a>
</h3>
<div class='post-header'>
<div class='post-header-line-1'></div>
</div>
<div class='post-body entry-content' id='post-body-7624480034298574806' itemprop='description articleBody'>
<p><strong></strong>
						

					

				
					</p><div class="feat_content clear-fix">

						
						

						

						<div class="feat_exc">
							
<figure class="wp-block-image"><a href="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEju-sC2sTifyp2CfVFz0S65urJnR0rHhQdP49Jfp5YgXfozLRxUmrave6uH8l9cBa93jfTpEaUk0PugrsHjmwtAHPXHjvLGYlSrHhsjegSL9q8hwyKwRnZBggPcbNCvh4E7a-NJ-B6LDdzLxkXCvbAUdrExX7POmBV63-pZDjHE8BPYDtZLfMYTLnoF/s1200/Flag_of_the_PLGA.svg.png"><img alt="" height="288" src="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEju-sC2sTifyp2CfVFz0S65urJnR0rHhQdP49Jfp5YgXfozLRxUmrave6uH8l9cBa93jfTpEaUk0PugrsHjmwtAHPXHjvLGYlSrHhsjegSL9q8hwyKwRnZBggPcbNCvh4E7a-NJ-B6LDdzLxkXCvbAUdrExX7POmBV63-pZDjHE8BPYDtZLfMYTLnoF/w488-h288/Flag_of_the_PLGA.svg.png" width="488" /></a></figure>



<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; COMMUNIST PARTY OF INDIA (MAOIST)</p>



<p><strong>Celebrate the 22nd Anniversary of PLGA!</strong><strong><br />Intensify Class struggle-Guerrilla war<br />Defeat &#8216;SAMADHAN&#8217; offensive and Advance People&#8217;s War!</strong></p>



<p><a></a><a></a><a></a><a></a><a></a><a></a><a></a><a></a> On the occasion of the 22nd Anniversary of PLGA on 2nd December 2022, the Central Committee<br />of the Communist Party of India (Maoist) calls upon the entire ranks of the party, PLGA units,<br />Revolutionary People&#8217;s Committees, Mass Organisations and Revolutionary people to grandly celebrate<br />in rural and urban areas all over the country with revolutionary enthusiasm. It calls upon to defeat the<br />counter revolutionary &#8216;SAMADHAN&#8217; offensive widen-intensify class struggle-guerrilla war, enhance the mass base and advance the People&#8217;s War.<br />On the occasion the CC conveys revolutionary greetings to the entire Party committees,<br />Commands, PLGA Commanders-fighters, Party members, Revolutionary People&#8217;s Committees, leaders- activists of Mass Organisations, members of People&#8217;s Militia and revolutionary people and to all the comrades of political, military, organisational, technical and cultural spheres. It hopes that the comrades injured in the guerrilla actions will recover soon.<br />The CMC pays humble revolutionary homage to the heroic guerrillas who laid down their lives in<br />the past one year. One hundred and thirty-two comrades became martyrs all over the country in a period<br />of 11 months.<br />The central and the state governments initiated the counter-revolutionary &#8216;SAMADHAN&#8217; strategic<br />offensive in 2017 May with a time limit of 5 years to eliminate the Indian Revolutionary Movement. With the objective to defeat the offensive PLGA took up People&#8217;s War-Guerrilla War in the leadership of our Party all through this period. We cannot separate the participation of people and people&#8217;s militia in this war. The central government reviewed the offensive last September and another action plan was adopted for one year.<br />PLGA held nearly 200 guerrilla war operations in the various guerrilla zones, red resistance areas<br />all over the country in the leadership of our party in a period of 11 months from 2021 December to 2022 November. Through these actions 31 police, Para-military and Commando forces were eliminated and 154 were injured. 7 modern arms and hundreds of rounds of ammunition and other war material were seized. 69 police informers, 7 political leaders of exploitive parties, 6 people&#8217;s enemies, 6 traitors were eliminated. Properties of the government and comprador bureaucratic capitalists were destroyed. PLGA forces resisted these forces in around 100 encounters.<br />On the whole, our PLGA forces made deliberate and opportunity ambushes, sniper actions, booby<br />trap, remote actions, sabotage actions on the armed forces of the enemy, seized their supplies, eliminated informers, counter revolutionaries, people&#8217;s enemies, shelled the police camps with improvised artillery and dug spike holes.<br />There are large scale people&#8217;s struggles in Dandakaranya and Bihar-Jharkhand for the past two<br />years against police camps, mines, roads-bridges, dams, police massacres and on the whole, against the<br />imperialist companies, comprador bureaucratic capitalist companies, against the central and the state<br />governments, against their local compradors and against corporatisation-militarisation. Thousands of<br />people are mobilising in these struggles..<br />People are struggling against the imperialist Multi-National Companies, the domestic comprador<br />capitalist corporate companies, the several kinds of basic infrastructure that the central and the state<br />governments proposes to build such as roads, dams, mines, power plants in many areas of the country<br />apart from the areas of movement. There are agitations for the release of political prisoners imprisoned<br />in conspiracy cases such as Bhima Koregaon and to withdraw fascist Acts such as UAPA.</p>



<p><a></a><a></a><a></a><a></a><a></a><a></a><a></a><a></a><a></a><a></a><a></a><a></a><a></a><a></a><a></a> Solidarity movement is growing in around 30 countries against the fascist offensive of the<br />comprador ruling classes on our party and revolutionary movement and in support of the People&#8217;s War<br />in India in the leadership of ICSPWI.<br />On the whole, class struggle relatively expanded and intensified. In the process, various kinds of<br />United forums are being formed leading to increasing participation in revolutionary movement and<br />support from friendly forces.<br />The central and the state governments deployed more than six and a half-lakh police, Para-<br />military and Commando forces in the areas of the movement. Since the beginning of 2020 to March 2021, CRPF established 23 Forward Operational Bases (FOB) in the country and 35 from 2021 March to 2022 March. The state had been using various kinds of drones for surveillance. It is organising lumpen youth into informers in the name of employment schemes.<br />In the international plane, although there are slight flexibilities in the economic crisis that is going<br />on since 2008, imperialist financial and economic crisis in intensifying. World Bank (WB) and International Monetary Fund (IMF) stated that the world economy is going into the mire of depression. One third of the world economy is estimated to decline this year or the next year and the three biggest economies, the US, EU and China shall stagnate. Imperialist globalisation policies are leading the proletariat in capitalist-imperialist countries into daily intensifying struggles.<br />BJP under the leadership of Narendra Modi is making severe attempts to transform India into a<br />&#8216;Hindu state&#8217; by 2047. Revolutionary-democratic forces, oppressed classes, oppressed social communities and oppressed nationalities must take up united, organised resistance movement and people&#8217;s war. This is the foremost, utmost important, main and immediate task of the Indian people.<br />The coming times would witness a spate of people&#8217;s struggles in the world and the country and<br />there shall be a third line of revolutions all over the world.<br />It is the responsibility of the vanguard Communist Party to politically enlighten the broad masses<br />and intensify class struggles and guerrilla war so as to achieve state power. We shall thus defeat the<br />counter-revolutionary &#8216;SAMADHAN&#8217; offensive of the enemy and advance the revolutionary movement.<br />We shall achieve the final victory.<br />On the occasion of the 22nd Anniversary of PLGA, hail the victories the PLGA in the leadership of<br />our party gained in the past one year. Hail the invincibility of the revolutionary movement that sustained resisting the counter revolutionary &#8216;SAMADHAN&#8217; offensive.<br />Abhay<br />Spokesperson<br />Central Commitee</p>



<p>&nbsp;28 November, 2022</p>
						</div>

					</div><p>&nbsp;</p>

color: #111111; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, FreeSans, sans-serif; font-size: 14.85px; line-height: 1.4; position: relative; width: 548px;"><strong>La
 polizia ha caricato gli operai che producono iPhone che protestavano 
per i bassi salari e le condizioni di lavoro mentre i casi di Covid&nbsp;</strong><strong>hanno&nbsp;</strong><strong>raggiun</strong><strong>to&nbsp;</strong><strong>livelli record in Cina</strong><p class="has-medium-font-size"><em>Gli
 agenti prendono a calci e colpiscono il personale dello stabilimento 
Foxconn di Zhengzhou, con Apple che lamenta ritardi nella consegna di 
iPhone 14</em></p><p class="has-medium-font-size">La polizia in Cina ha 
picchiato gli operai che protestavano per le condizioni di lavoro e 
bassi salari nella piÃ¹ grande fabbrica di iPhone, mentre i casi di 
Covid-19 del paese hanno raggiunto un nuovo massimo giornaliero.<br />I 
video online hanno mostrato migliaia di persone con la mascherina di 
fronte a file di poliziotti in tute protettive bianche con scudi 
antisommossa di plastica. La polizia ha preso a calci e colpito un 
manifestante con dei bastoni dopo che questi aveva afferrato un palo di 
metallo che era stato usato per colpirlo. Le persone che hanno 
realizzato il filmato hanno affermato che Ã¨ stato girato sul sito.</p><a name="more"></a><p></p><p></p><p class="has-medium-font-size"><br />La
 protesta a Zhengzhou Ã¨ durata fino a mercoledÃ¬ mattina quando migliaia 
di operai si sono radunati fuori dai dormitori e hanno affrontato gli 
addetti alla sicurezza della fabbrica, secondo Li. Altri video 
mostravano manifestanti che usavano degli estintori contro la polizia.<br />Foxconn,
 il piÃ¹ grande assemblatore a contratto di smartphone e altri 
dispositivi elettronici, sta lottando per riuscire ad evadere gli ordini
 per l&#8217;iPhone 14 dopo che migliaia di dipendenti hanno lasciato la 
fabbrica nella cittÃ  centrale di Zhengzhou il mese scorso dopo le 
lamentele sulle condizioni di lavoro non sicure.<br />Secondo un 
dipendente, Li Sanshan, le proteste sono iniziate martedÃ¬ dopo che gli 
operai che avevano percorso lunghe distanze per accettare un lavoro in 
fabbrica si sono lamentati del fatto che l&#8217;azienda ha cambiato i termini
 della loro retribuzione.<br />Li ha detto di aver lasciato un lavoro di 
catering quando ha visto un annuncio che prometteva 25.000 yuan ($ 
3.500) per due mesi di lavoro. Che sarebbe significativamente al di 
sopra della retribuzione media per questo tipo di lavoro nella zona. Ma 
dopo che i dipendenti sono arrivati, la societÃ  ha detto loro che 
avrebbero dovuto lavorare altri due mesi con una paga inferiore per 
ricevere i 25.000 yuan, secondo quanto sostiene Li.<br />&#8220;Foxconn ha 
pubblicizzato offerte di salario molto allettanti e molti operai sono 
arrivati da tutte le parti del paese, solo per scoprire che venivano 
presi in giro&#8221;, ha continuato Li.<br />Foxconn ha dichiarato giovedÃ¬ che un &#8220;errore tecnico&#8221; Ã¨ stato responsabile della confusione sulla retribuzione e si Ã¨ scusata.<br />Un
 uomo che si Ã¨ identificato come il segretario del partito comunista 
responsabile dei servizi alla comunitÃ  Ã¨ stato mostrato in un video, 
pubblicato sulla piattaforma di social media Sina Weibo, esortare i 
manifestanti a ritirarsi. Ha assicurato loro che le loro richieste 
sarebbero state soddisfatte.<br />Le proteste arrivano in mezzo a una 
forte frustrazione per le restrizioni Covid nelle aree della Cina che 
hanno chiuso negozi e uffici e confinato milioni di persone nelle loro 
case.<br />GiovedÃ¬ la Cina ha riportato il numero piÃ¹ alto di nuovi casi di Covid, con 31.444 nuove infezioni.<br />Sebbene
 il numero di casi e decessi sia relativamente basso rispetto agli altri
 Paesi, il Partito comunista cinese rimane impegnato nella sua strategia
 &#8220;zero-Covid&#8221; che mira a isolare ogni caso ed eliminare completamente il
 virus.<br />MercoledÃ¬, il governo ha ordinato un blocco effettivo di 
diversi distretti di Zhengzhou, con i residenti del centro cittÃ  non 
autorizzati ad andarsene a meno che non abbiano un test Covid negativo e
 il permesso delle autoritÃ . Le restrizioni, che dureranno cinque giorni
 dalla mezzanotte di venerdÃ¬, interessano piÃ¹ di sei milioni di persone,
 circa la metÃ  della popolazione della cittÃ .<br />Il governo sta cercando
 di contenere l&#8217;ultima ondata di focolai senza chiudere le fabbriche e 
il resto della sua economia come ha fatto all&#8217;inizio del 2020. Le sue 
tattiche includono la &#8220;gestione a circuito chiuso&#8221; in base alla quale 
gli operai vivono nelle loro fabbriche senza alcun contatto esterno.<br />Lo
 status della Cina come potenza di esportazione si basa su fabbriche 
come quella di Foxconn che assemblano l&#8217;elettronica di consumo mondiale,
 i giocattoli e altri beni.<br />Apple ha avvertito che le consegne di 
iPhone 14 sarebbero state ritardate dopo che l&#8217;accesso a una zona 
industriale intorno alla fabbrica di Zhengzhou &#8211; che secondo Foxconn 
impiega 200.000 operai &#8211; Ã¨ stato sospeso a causa di epidemie.<br />La societÃ  non ha risposto immediatamente a una richiesta di commento sulle ultime proteste.</p></div>
<div style='clear: both;'></div>

<h2 class='date-header'><span>domingo, 20 de noviembre de 2022</span></h2>

<div class='post-outer'>
<div class='post hentry uncustomized-post-template' itemprop='blogPost' itemscope='itemscope' itemtype='http://schema.org/BlogPosting'>

<h3 class='post-title entry-title' itemprop='name'>
<a href='http://dazibaorojo08.blogspot.com/2022/11/brasilviva-heroica-luta-das-mulheres.html'>BRASIL:VIVA A HERÃICA LUTA DAS MULHERES NEGRAS BRASILEIRAS! (MFP)</a>
</h3>
<div class='post-header'>
<div class='post-header-line-1'></div>
</div>
<div class='post-body entry-content' id='post-body-7695550647383005415' itemprop='description articleBody'>
<p align="justify" style="line-height: 115%; margin-bottom: 0.28cm;"><span style="font-family: arial;">&nbsp;<b><span style="color: red;"></span></b><span style="color: black;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="letter-spacing: normal;"><span style="background: transparent;">O</span></span></span></span><span style="color: black;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="letter-spacing: normal;"><span style="background: transparent;">
mÃªs de novembro marcar a luta do povo preto, </span></span></span></span><span style="color: black;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="letter-spacing: normal;"><span style="background: transparent;">por
esse motivo</span></span></span></span><span style="color: black;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="letter-spacing: normal;"><span style="background: transparent;">
o Movimento Feminino Popular &#8211; MFP, vem homenagear </span></span></span></span><span style="color: black;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="letter-spacing: normal;"><span style="background: transparent;">algumas</span></span></span></span><span style="color: black;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="letter-spacing: normal;"><span style="background: transparent;">
mulheres negras que fizeram histÃ³ria na luta do povo brasileiro.
</span></span></span></span><span style="color: black;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="letter-spacing: normal;"><span style="background: transparent;">Certamente
hÃ¡ muitÃ­ssimas outras, sÃ£o herÃ³inas desconhecidas, intelectuais
progressistas e lutadoras simples do povo, e segue como tarefa das
revolucionÃ¡rias do Brasil descobrir e levantar seus estadartes.</span></span></span></span></span></p><span style="font-family: arial;">

</span><p align="center" style="line-height: 115%; margin-bottom: 0.28cm;"><span style="font-family: arial;"><span style="color: red;"><span style="font-size: x-small;"><b><span style="letter-spacing: normal;"><span style="background: transparent;">M</span></span><span style="letter-spacing: normal;"><span style="background: transparent;">ORTE
AO RACISMO!</span></span></b></span></span></span></p><span style="font-family: arial;"><span style="color: red;">
</span></span><p align="center" style="letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 115%; margin-bottom: 0.28cm;">
<span style="font-family: arial;"><span style="color: red;"><span style="font-size: x-small;"><b><span style="background: transparent;">VIVA
A LUTA DO POVO PRETO!</span></b></span></span></span></p><span style="font-family: arial;">
</span><p align="justify" style="line-height: 115%; margin-bottom: 0.28cm;"><span style="font-family: arial;"><span style="color: black;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="letter-spacing: normal;"><span style="background: transparent;">O</span></span></span></span><span style="color: black;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="letter-spacing: normal;"><span style="background: transparent;">
racismo, opressÃ£o vivida por mais da metade da populaÃ§Ã£o </span></span></span></span><span style="color: black;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="letter-spacing: normal;"><span style="background: transparent;">do
Brasil</span></span></span></span><span style="color: black;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="letter-spacing: normal;"><span style="background: transparent;">,
tem suas raÃ­zes </span></span></span></span><span style="color: black;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="letter-spacing: normal;"><span style="background: transparent;">f</span></span></span></span><span style="color: black;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="letter-spacing: normal;"><span style="background: transparent;">i</span></span></span></span><span style="color: black;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="letter-spacing: normal;"><span style="background: transparent;">n</span></span></span></span><span style="color: black;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="letter-spacing: normal;"><span style="background: transparent;">cadas
em mais de </span></span></span></span><span style="color: black;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="letter-spacing: normal;"><span style="background: transparent;">cinco</span></span></span></span><span style="color: black;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="letter-spacing: normal;"><span style="background: transparent;">

</p><span style="font-family: arial;">
</span><p align="justify" style="letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 115%; margin-bottom: 0.28cm;">
<span style="font-family: arial;"><span style="color: black;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="background: transparent;">Natural
de Sacramento, Minas Gerais, Carolina Maria de Jesus nasceu em 14 de
marÃ§o de 1914. De origem muito humilde, neta de escravos e filha de
uma lavadeira, desde crianÃ§a manifestava o desejo de aprender a ler
e escrever. Aos 7 anos de idade, passou a frequentar a escola, mas
apÃ³s cursar a segunda sÃ©rie do primÃ¡rio, teve de abandonar a
escola, pois sua mÃ£e nÃ£o tinha condiÃ§Ãµes de prover para ela e
seus 7 irmÃ£os. Sempre passando dificuldades, fome, frio e sem lugar
fixo para morar, Carolina de Jesus passou parte da infÃ¢ncia morando
em diversas cidades do interior de SÃ£o Paulo. Dizem que por sua
rebeldia natural, nÃ£o se adaptou ao trabalho de empregada domÃ©stica
quando chegou a SÃ£o Paulo em 1947. GrÃ¡vida, chegou a morar na rua
por nÃ£o concederem trabalho Ã  mulheres grÃ¡vidas na Ã©poca. Foi
assim que chegou Ã  favela do CanindÃ©, fruto de uma polÃ­tica
higienista do governador de SÃ£o Paulo Ã  Ã©poca, Adhemar de Barros. </span></span></span></span>
</p><span style="font-family: arial;">
</span><p align="justify" style="letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 115%; margin-bottom: 0.28cm;">
<span style="font-family: arial;"><span style="color: black;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="background: transparent;">Construiu
seu prÃ³prio barraco e criou lÃ¡ seus filhos. Carolina dizia que
nenhum homem entenderia sua necessidade literÃ¡ria, referindo-se aos
pais de seus filhos que a abandonara para criÃ¡-los sozinha, pois
estava sempre buscando escrever e ler. Nos anos de 1960, Carolina de
Jesus lanÃ§ou seu maior sucesso literÃ¡rio O Quarto de Despejo, no
qual conseguiu certa ascensÃ£o social e prestÃ­gio. Chegou a lanÃ§ar
um LP com suas mÃºsicas autorais. Entretanto, seus outros livros nÃ£o
tiveram o mesmo destaque e Carolina teve de voltar a catar papel para
sobreviver. Carolina de Jesus morreu vivendo de maneira humilde em 13
de fevereiro de 1977, com 63 anos, em Parelheiros, lanÃ§ada Ã 
invisibilidade e ao esquecimento pelo mercado editorial.&nbsp;</span></span></span></span></p><p align="center" style="line-height: 115%; margin-bottom: 0.28cm;"><span style="font-family: arial;"><span style="color: red;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="letter-spacing: normal;"><b><span style="background: transparent;">Marli
Pereira Soares</span></b></span></span></span><span style="color: black;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="letter-spacing: normal;"><span style="background: transparent;">
</span></span></span></span></span>
</p><span style="font-family: arial;">
</span><p align="center" style="letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 115%; margin-bottom: 0.28cm;">
<span style="font-family: arial;"><img alt="" src="data:image/png;base64," /> <br /></span>

</p><span style="font-family: arial;">
</span><p align="justify" style="letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 115%; margin-bottom: 0.28cm;">
<span style="font-family: arial;"><span style="color: black;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="background: transparent;">Marli
Pereira Soares, ou Marli Coragem como era conhecida, nasceu no Rio de
Janeiro em 25 de outubro de 1954. Trabalhou como empregada domÃ©stica
e aos 12 anos de idade, viu a favela que crescera ser alvo de um
incÃªndio criminoso. Nos anos de 1979, durante o regime militar,
presenciou uma invasÃ£o das tropas da polÃ­cia militar Ã  sua casa,
que resultou na execuÃ§Ã£o de seu irmÃ£o, Paulo Pereira Soares. Marli
chegou a ir na 20Âª delegacia de polÃ­cia, em Belford Roxo, na
Baixada Fluminense, onde reconheceu os assassino de seu irmÃ£o, que
nunca foram preso ou punidos pelo crime que cometeram. </span></span></span></span>
</p><span style="font-family: arial;">
</span><p align="justify" style="letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 115%; margin-bottom: 0.28cm;">
<span style="font-family: arial;"><span style="color: black;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="background: transparent;">A
partir deste fato, Marli passou a denunciar os crimes do velho
estado, sob o regime militar e tambÃ©m apÃ³s a falsa
"redemocratizaÃ§Ã£o". Marli se tornou uma firme ativista da
luta contra os grupos de extermÃ­nio e contra a impunidade e chegou a
receber ameaÃ§as por nÃ£o se calar. 14 anos apÃ³s o vil assassinato
de seu irmÃ£o, Marli viu o filho de apenas 15 anos, Sandro, ser
morto. Mesmo diante da dor do luto, Marli o transformou em forÃ§as
para luta e lutou a vida inteira por justiÃ§a.&nbsp;</span></span></span></span>
</p><span style="font-family: arial;">
</span><p align="center" style="line-height: 115%; margin-bottom: 0.28cm;"><span style="font-family: arial;"><span style="color: red;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="letter-spacing: normal;"><b><span style="background: transparent;">ConceiÃ§Ã£o
Evaristo</span></b></span></span></span><span style="color: black;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="letter-spacing: normal;"><span style="background: transparent;">
</span></span></span></span></span>
</p><span style="font-family: arial;">
</span><p align="center" style="letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 115%; margin-bottom: 0.28cm;">
<span style="font-family: arial;"><img alt="" height="218" src="data:image/png;base64," width="328" /> <br /></span>

</p><span style="font-family: arial;">
</span><p align="justify" style="letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 115%; margin-bottom: 0.28cm;">
<span style="font-family: arial;"><span style="color: black;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="background: transparent;">Nascida
em Belo Horizonte, em 29 de novembro de 1946, Maria ConceiÃ§Ã£o
Evaristo Ã© uma grande expoente da literatura brasileira, sobretudo
porque aborda em suas obras reflexÃµes e denÃºncias sobre a
desigualdade social e racial, alÃ©m de escrever sobre a condiÃ§Ã£o
das mulheres negras no Brasil. Segunda de nove filhos, teve a
infÃ¢ncia e adolescÃªncia marcadas pela misÃ©ria. Trabalhou como
empregada domÃ©stica ao mesmo tempo em que se dedicava aos estudos,
aspirando ser professora. ConceiÃ§Ã£o concluiu o curso normal, aos 25
anos e  mudou-se para o Rio de Janeiro para cursar Letras na UFRJ,
formando-se em 1990, mesmo ano que lanÃ§ou sua primeira obra
literÃ¡ria intitulada "Cadernos Negros". ConceiÃ§Ã£o
adquiriu tÃ­tulo de mestre em literatura pela PUC-Rio e de doutora
pela UFF, alÃ©m de ter lecionado em diversas escolas e universidades.
ConceiÃ§Ã£o Evaristo Ã© uma das principais expressÃµes literÃ¡rias
brasileiras da contemporaneidade. </span></span></span></span>
</p>

<h2 class='title'>Citas del Presidente Mao Tse-Tung</h2>
<div class='widget-content'>
Colocar los problemas sobre la mesa.<br/>Esto lo deben hacer no solo el "jefe  de la escuadra", sino tambien los miembros del comitÃ©. No se debe hablar a espaldas de la gente. Cuando surge algÃºn problema, hay que convocar una reuniÃ³n y colocar el problema sobre la mesa para discutirlo y tomar decisiones, y asÃ­ el problema serÃ¡ resuelto.<br/>Si existen problemas y no se colocan encima de la mesa, permanceran sin resolver por largo tiempo y hasta pueden seguir pendientes durante aÃ±os.<br/>Entre el "jefe de escuadra" y los miembros del comitÃ© debe haber mutua comprensiÃ³n. Nada hay mÃ¡s importante que la comprensiÃ³n, el apoyo y la amistad entre el secretario y los miembros del comitÃ©, entre el ComitÃ© Central y sus burÃ³s, asÃ­ como entre Ã©stos y los comitÃ©s regionales del Partido.<br/><em></em><br/><br/><em>"Metodos de trabajo en los comitÃ©s del Partido."(13 marzo de 1949 ). Obras Escogidas, tomo IV.</em><br/><br/>

    window.followersIframe = null;
    function followersIframeOpen(url) {
      gapi.load("gapi.iframes", function() {
        if (gapi.iframes && gapi.iframes.getContext) {
          window.followersIframe = gapi.iframes.getContext().openChild({
            url: url,

              },

              },

            }
          });
        }
      });
    }
